text:
I was really fortunate to have you as one my roommates. Bhut kuch sikhne ko mila tmse bhai. Sayad tm na milte to mera ek bhi dassa ni aa pata kyuki tujhe dekh ke hi to inspiration mila tha bhai. 
Agar koi galti hui ho to I am extremely sorry. Bas mujhe hamesha yaad rakhna itni badi duniya meğŸ˜…
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text:
Gupta ji ke baare me kya hi batae. Hr course me grade aane se phle rote hy ki D aa rha, fail ho jayenge aur jb marks aati hy to pata chalta hy ki bhaia ji to topper nikle :P. OAT se suru hui dosti job tk sath chal rhi aur hamesha chalte rahegi. OAT me pizza aur roll party hamesha yaad aaegi jo hmlog aksar kiya krte the. Bhai hamesha itna sath dene ke liye Thanks aur ha civil me competition dene ke liye bhi warna meri CPI kabhi itni ho ni paati.
Ek baat aur bolunga, ladkiyo ki line lagi rhti hy aapko propose krne ke liye, aapke jaisi kiskmat kha hy sbki.
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text: Bhai tu bhut chill banda hy. Tere sath baat krke maza aata hy. Kafi positive lagta hy. Bs aise ki chaapte rhna. Best of Luck ğŸ‘
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text: Chaapu Bhai! Placement me chaapne ke liye. Bhai tere se sach me bahut motivation milta hy. Jaisa tera dedication hy na tujhe wo bahut aage le jaega. Abhi to bs suruat hy. Bs lage rho. Aur ha apne is dost ko bhulna mt chahe kitna bhi busy ho jao life me. I will always be there.
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text:
HSBC phodne wale! Bhai apke jaisa dedication khi ni dekha IITK me. Intern lagne ke baad bhi din bhar DS Algo ki book lekar padhna. Itni dur ka sochte ho bhai. Tujshe motivate hoke maine bhi kharid liya tha lekin palat ke dekha bhi ni hoga kabhiğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. 
Yar tu akhand chaapu hy. #MSEtopper. Aise hi chaapte rhna. Touch me rhna bhai.
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text: One of my greatest friend! Ha hmari dosti thodi late hui thi almost 1-1.5 yrs baad lekin tere jaisa friend koi aur ni hy. Thanks IP hamesha support krne ke liye aur hr wo group project me sath dene ke liye jo hmne sath me kiye. Bhai wo sare labs jo hmne kiye sath me kya maza aati thi. Those will still be the most memorable moments of my life. Yar IP bus ye dosti hamesha bnae rkhna kyuki tere jaise dost bhut muskil se milte hy zindagi me.
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text: Ha hmari dosti 1-1.5 saal baad hui thi lekin you are one of my greatest friend of my life! Thanks IP hamesha support aur motivate krne ke liye aur hr wo group project me sath dene ke liye jo hmne sath me kiye. Bhai wo sare civil ke labs jisme mai, tm aur Abhishek sath hote the, kya maza aati thi. Those will be still the best moments of my life. Bs IP hamesha ye dosti nibahte rahna kyuki tere jaise dost bahut muskil se milte hy zindagi me.

text:
Yar tu IITK me mujhe sbse alag laga. Pura sem game khelte ho aur last moment me padh ke chaapte ho bhai. Ultimate bro! 
Yar tu bhut helpful hy maine jab bhi tujshe kuch bhi pucha tune hamesha bataya hy. Thanks for that. Always be like that because that's unique about youğŸ˜

text: You are the most humble guy I have ever seen in my life. Always keep smiling. Be in touch always.
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text: Is baar jara tez bolde last time hyğŸ˜‚ Bhai itna silent rh kr bhi kya mst sense of humar hy tera. Kaise kr lete ho ye sbğŸ˜… Tere jokes hamesha yaad aaenge. Bas aise hi lage rho aur chaapte rhoğŸ‘

text: Dassa Boi! Aakir tune apna jalwa dikha hi diya. Thoda der aaye lekin durust aaye. Bhai suru me hmari utni baat ni hui thi lekin fir second year se tere se jaan pehchaan hui. Yar tu bhut cool banda hy. Bhale tu thoda saant rhta hy log teri maarte bhi hyğŸ˜‚, but tu mst rhta hy. Aise hi lage rho, chaapte rho abhi to 1 saal aur hy tere paas.

text: Aapke jaisa chaapu kha hy koi chahe core ho ya non-core. Thanks bhai project me sath dene ke liye. Bhai bhulna mt. Kabhi kabhar msg kr dena haal chal ke liye
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text:
Cool boy!! Sach me bhai teri dedication ka koi comparison ni hy. Hamesha help krne ke liye ready rhte ho. Bhai tu bahut chaapu hy. 
Although hamari sath me utni memories ni hy but I am lucky to have you as one my friends.
Always keep smiling.
author: Ashutosh  Ranjan

text: You have been one of my good friends. I remember discussing about my PPO and placement with you ğŸ˜…. Thank you for guiding me. Thank you once again for taking lead in group projects in 7th sem which was very crucial for placement. It helped to prepare well for placements.
